# isEnabled

**Instance Property**

A Boolean value that specifies whether the sharing service picker item is enabled.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor var isEnabled: Bool { get set }
```

## Discussion

If [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/true], the sharing button is enabled.

If the sharing popover is currently visible when this property is changed to [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/false], the popover is dismissed.
